      <title>迈阿密国际队因球星缺席和2-1获胜而令白帽队球迷失望</title>
      <link>https://apnews.com/article/inter-miami-vancouver-whitecaps-mls-cb1814d32bb0ba6d819e5a88c8dcd8bd</link>
